description: The Nasdaq Global Artificial Intelligence and Big Data Total Net Return Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large, mid and small-cap companies from global developed and emerging markets that have material exposure to themes related to among other AI, big data and cyber security that meet certain ESG Criteria Up to 100 companies are selected for inclusion Individual securities are capped at 4.5% and the index follows a market capitalization weighting methodology Reviewed on a semiannual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.indexes.nasdaqomx.com
name: Xtrackers Artificial Intelligence & Big Data UCITS ETF 1C
